/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=html5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Blindness_resistance rootpage-Blindness_resistance skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Blindness resistance</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Blindness resistance</b> is a type of resistance <a href=\"/wiki/Property\" title=\"Property\">property</a> that appears in <i><a href=\"/wiki/NetHack\" title=\"NetHack\">NetHack</a></i>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Description\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Description</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#dNetHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">dNetHack</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Description\">Description</span></h2>\n<p>Blindness resistance prevents protects a <a href=\"/wiki/Hero\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hero\">hero</a> or <a href=\"/wiki/Monster\" title=\"Monster\">monster</a> from light-related sources of <a href=\"/wiki/Blindness\" title=\"Blindness\">blindness</a>:<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li>The blinding <a href=\"/wiki/Explosion_attack\" title=\"Explosion attack\">explosion attack</a> of a <a href=\"/wiki/Yellow_light\" title=\"Yellow light\">yellow light</a></li>\n<li>The blinding <a href=\"/wiki/Gaze_attack\" title=\"Gaze attack\">gaze attack</a> of an <a href=\"/wiki/Archon\" title=\"Archon\">Archon</a></li>\n<li>The flash of an <a href=\"/wiki/Expensive_camera\" title=\"Expensive camera\">expensive camera</a></li>\n<li>The blinding effects of <a href=\"/wiki/Lightning\" title=\"Lightning\">lightning</a></li>\n<li>The blinding portion of the <a href=\"/wiki/Magic_trap\" title=\"Magic trap\">magic trap</a> effect that creates monsters</li></ul>\n<p>The property can only be obtained via the following sources:<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Being unconscious, blinded or <a href=\"/wiki/Asleep\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Asleep\">asleep</a>, or being an <a href=\"/wiki/Eyeless\" title=\"Eyeless\">eyeless</a> monster<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Being a monster that has a blinding explosion attack (i.e. a yellow light)<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Being a monster that has a blinding gaze attack (i.e. an Archon)<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Wield\" title=\"Wield\">Wielding</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Sunsword\" title=\"Sunsword\">Sunsword</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p>Wearing <a href=\"/wiki/The_Eyes_of_the_Overworld\" title=\"The Eyes of the Overworld\">The Eyes of the Overworld</a> does not grant blindness resistance, but overrides the effects of blindness and allows the wearer to see via <a href=\"/wiki/Astral_vision\" title=\"Astral vision\">astral vision</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"dNetHack\">dNetHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/DNetHack\" title=\"DNetHack\">dNetHack</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/NotdNetHack\" title=\"NotdNetHack\">notdNetHack</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/NotnotdNetHack\" title=\"NotnotdNetHack\">notnotdNetHack</a>, blindness resistance can apply to some other forms of blindness, and can be obtained from several other sources:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Wielding any of the <a href=\"/wiki/DNetHack_artifacts#Artifacts_of_the_Empyrial_Lords\" title=\"DNetHack artifacts\">Artifacts of the Empyrial Lords</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Invoking\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Invoking\">Invoking</a> <a href=\"/wiki/DNetHack_artifacts#The_Shield_of_the_All-Seeing\" title=\"DNetHack artifacts\">The Shield of the All-Seeing</a></li></ul>\n<p>A hero is completely immune to blindness while the <a href=\"/wiki/Spirits_(dNetHack)\" title=\"Spirits (dNetHack)\">spirit</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Dantalion\" title=\"Dantalion\">Dantalion</a> is bound, but only if they are not <a href=\"/wiki/Wear\" title=\"Wear\">wearing</a> a <a href=\"/wiki/Shirt\" title=\"Shirt\">shirt</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Suit\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Suit\">suit</a> or <a href=\"/wiki/Cloak\" title=\"Cloak\">cloak</a> that covers the extra faces on their body.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/mondata.c#L146\">src/mondata.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 146</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/mondata.c#L148\">src/mondata.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 148</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/mondata.c#L156\">src/mondata.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 156</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/mondata.c#L163\">src/mondata.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 163</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/mondata.c#L164\">src/mondata.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 164</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/Net